## Status Definitions

- `PENDING` — Promise made, no further action taken yet.
- `CALENDAR NEEDED` — Promise involves a date/time and should become a calendar event. Picked up by the daily commitment-to-calendar sweep.
- `IN PROGRESS` — Work has started.
- `WAITING` — On someone else (used in "They Said They Would" section).
- `DONE` — Completed. Acknowledged via mailto link, digital trace (sent message, calendar event), or self-report.
- `OVERDUE` — Past expected date with no status change. Surfaced loudly in morning briefings.
